no.geosoft.jwlf

Class JsonTable

  • java.lang.Object
    • no.geosoft.jwlf.JsonTable

  • public final class JsonTable
extends Object
    Class for modeling a JSON table. Useful for holding metadata originating from old well log formats like DLIS, LIS, LAS etc.

    The JSON table has the following structure: 

       "<name>" : {
     "attributes": ["<attr1>", "<attr2>", "<attr3>", ... "<attrn>"],
     "objects": [
       "<object1>": [<v11>, <v12>, <v13>, ... <v1n>],
       "<object2>": [<v21>, <v22>, <v23>, ... <v2n>],
       "<object3>": [<v31>, <v32>, <v33>, ... <v3n>],
       :
       "<objectm>": [<vm1>, <vm2>, <vm3>, ... <vmn>]
     ]
   }
    Note that each value is a primitive item or an array of primitive items.
    Author:
    Jacob Dreyer
